ttp://bgm.tv/ep/121162","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"And the Break-Up Scene","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2011-09-26","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":121163,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/121163","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"And Strokes of Goodwill","name_cn":"","duration":"0:21:13","airdate":"2011-10-03","comment":2,"desc":"Max带Caroline去跳蚤商店购物，两人为争夺一件T恤衫互不相让。","status":"Air"},{"id":121164,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/121164","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"And the Rich People Problems","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2011-10-10","comment":2,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":121165,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/121165","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"And the '90's Horse Party","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2011-10-17","comment":1,"desc":"为了给蛋糕生意筹资启动资金，Caroline和Max决定举办一个90年代主题宴会，以吸引嬉皮士富翁的注意。Caroline发现自己的前男友竟然也来了，立刻变得六神无主。","status":"Air"},{"id":121166,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/121166","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"And the Disappearing Bed","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2011-10-24","comment":2,"desc":"Caroline想在Max的公寓里替自己安装一张墨菲床（一种不用时可折起放进壁橱的床）。与此同时，Max和Johnny之间的「化学反应」越来越强烈。","status":"Air"},{"id":121167,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/121167","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"And the Pretty Problem","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2011-10-31","comment":2,"desc":"Caroline拉着Max和她一起参加「蛋糕美化班」，希望以此来提升她们制作蛋糕的水平，推动她们的蛋糕生意「再上新台阶」。","status":"Air"},{"id":121168,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/121168","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"And Hoarder Culture","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2011-11-07","comment":2,"desc":"为了多挣点钱，Max和Caroline接下一份清洁工作。但她们没料到这间公寓的主人是个囤积狂，乱七八糟的杂物差点把她们淹没！与此同时，Max发现Johnny对她隐瞒了一个秘密。","status":"Air"},{"id":121169,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/121169","type":0,"sort":9,"name":"And The Really Petty Cash","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2011-11-14","comment":2,"desc":"Johnny的女友Cashandra准备将Johnny的画拿到她的艺术展览会上展出，还请来Max和Caroline为展览会制作蛋糕，但两人很快意识到Cashandra绝非善意！","status":"Air"},{"id":121170,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/121170","type":0,"sort":10,"name":"And the Very Christmas Thanksgiving","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2011-11-21","comment":2,"desc":"休假季到来了，但Caroline和Max为了赚更多的钱，不得不放弃休息时间去一家百货公司的「圣诞主题区」打临工。这是Caroline破产后度过的第一个假期！","status":"Air"},{"id":121171,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/121171","type":0,"sort":11,"name":"And the Reality Check","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2011-12-05","comment":1,"desc":"为了让Caroline的马儿Chestnut有个合适的地方过冬，Max和Caroline决定替它找份差事。与此同时，雇佣Max当保姆的Peach决定报名参加真人秀《TriBeCa娇妻》（Real Housewives of TriBeCa）。TriBeCa是曼哈顿南部的一个住宅和商业区。","status":"Air"},{"id":121172,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/121172","type":0,"sort":12,"name":"And the Pop-Up Sale","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2011-12-12","comment":2,"desc":"Max的烤炉坏了，Caroline决定将一些昂贵的首饰还给Barney的百货公司，换回足够的钱来买新烤箱。Caroline很快发现自己早就被「除名」了，无奈之下，她只好在厕所里举行临时「珠宝拍卖会」。","status":"Air"},{"id":121173,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/121173","type":0,"sort":13,"name":"And the Secret Ingredient","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2012-01-02","comment":3,"desc":"Caroline对收集购物优惠券着了迷。与此同时，Caroline发现了Max制作蛋糕的绝密配方。注：《超级优惠券迷》和《绝密配方》是两部人气很高的真人秀节目，不知道本集是不是在影射这两部真人秀。","status":"Air"},{"id":121174,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/121174","type":0,"sort":14,"name":"And the Upstairs Neighbor","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2012-01-16","comment":2,"desc":"Max和Caroline楼上的老租户死了，她们对新搬来的人戒心重重，甚至怀疑其与老租户之死有关。","status":"Air"},{"id":121175,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/121175","type":0,"sort":15,"name":"And The Blind Spot","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2012-02-06","comment":3,"desc":"Sophie决定考验Max和Caroline是否具备足够的「清洁技能」－她当然不想雇佣两个什么都不会的「笨女佣」来毁掉自己的清洁生意！","status":"Air"},{"id":121176,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/121176","type":0,"sort":16,"name":"And the Broken Hearts","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2012-02-13","comment":4,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":121177,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/121177","type":0,"sort":17,"name":"And The Kosher Cupcakes","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2012-02-20","comment":1,"desc":"Max和Caroline准备在一个犹太少年成年礼上销售她们的蛋糕，但麻烦的是……她们必须首先让这些蛋糕符合犹太教的规定。","status":"Air"},{"id":121178,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/121178","type":0,"sort":18,"name":"And The One-Night Stands","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2012-02-27","comment":3,"desc":"Caroline让Max陪她去监狱探望父亲。","status":"Air"},{"id":121179,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/121179","type":0,"sort":19,"name":"And The Spring Break","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2012-03-19","comment":3,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":121180,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/121180","type":0,"sort":20,"name":"And The Drug Money","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2012-04-09","comment":1,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":121181,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/121181","type":0,"sort":21,"name":"And the Messy Purse Smackdown","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2012-04-16","comment":4,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":121182,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/121182","type":0,"sort":22,"name":"And The Big Buttercream Breakthrough","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2012-04-30","comment":2,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":121183,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/121183","type":0,"sort":23,"name":"And Martha Stewart Have A Ball (1)","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2012-05-07","comment":1,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":121184,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/121184","type":0,"sort":24,"name":"And Martha Stewart Have A Ball (2)","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2012-05-07","comment":1,"desc":"Max和Caroline来到纽约大都会艺术博物馆参加一个盛大的时装发布会。她们欣喜地见到了美国媒体大亨、女富豪Martha Stewart（自己扮演自己），决心要让她品尝一下她们做的蛋糕－－如果Martha Stewart对蛋糕满意的话，说不定她们的「25万美元」梦想就要提前实现了……Martha Stewart本身也是个厨艺大师，要想糊弄她可不容易！","status":"Air"}],"crt":[{"id":28441,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/fe/1c/28441_crt_NnnNT.jpg","name":"Han Lee","desc":"配角"}],"staff":[{"id":39893,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/64/e2/39893_prsn_Awgzh.jpg","name":"尼克·詹姆森","desc":"配角"}],"relations":[{"id":49664,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/f3/e1/49664_va71L.jpg","title":"2 Broke Girls (Season 2)","type":"续集","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/49664"}],"like":[{"id":4178,"name":"摩登家庭 第一季","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/15/58/4178_0pilZ.jpg"},{"id":9464,"nam